Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.34,0:00:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\N Just Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.54,0:00:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.01,0:00:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.55,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.66,0:00:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.87,0:00:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.67,0:00:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.95,0:01:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.39,0:01:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.06,0:01:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.70,0:01:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.40,0:01:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.28,0:01:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特爾?怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.28,0:01:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你告訴大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.78,0:01:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要在我面前出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.25,0:01:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.99,0:01:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會殺死大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.56,0:01:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過不要接近我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.26,0:01:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想說的只有這些話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.71,0:01:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果一切都瘋狂的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.24,0:01:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就會相信自己而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.91,0:02:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特爾，我要殺死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.62,0:02:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二十五話\N[卡特爾對希洛]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.19,0:03:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防護罩也到了極限嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.46,0:03:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.46,0:03:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們為何在戰鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.40,0:03:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衛星和OZ聯手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.40,0:03:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衛星變成敵人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.41,0:03:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對特洛瓦和希洛你們來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.44,0:03:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衛星也是敵人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙瘋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.25,0:03:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要把一切毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧?希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會死啊，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.87,0:04:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不想打倒同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.80,0:04:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我求你，快逃，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.84,0:04:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽到嗎?希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的背後有衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.44,0:04:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經很討厭那個衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.41,0:04:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和鋼彈交戰中的宇宙里歐部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.18,0:04:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,及特洛瓦‧巴頓駕駛的拜葉特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有回音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.55,0:04:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,推測和麥丘留士一起全軍覆沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衛星呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衛星毀滅了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.53,0:05:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒，衛星沒有很大的損毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.80,0:05:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，戰鬥還在繼續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護衛星而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.57,0:05:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真正鋼彈駕駛員的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.44,0:05:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能阻止新鋼彈的行動就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.98,0:05:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里歐的母艦有影像進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，把這些資料送去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.75,0:05:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月面基地的鋼彈技師手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.95,0:05:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該能得到些情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.62,0:05:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特校，現在聯絡不到月面基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.99,0:05:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.83,0:05:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茲巴洛夫技師長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.00,0:05:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴爾吉要求打開通訊線路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有聯絡進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.67,0:05:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.40,0:05:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾麥優侯爵的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.17,0:05:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是叫我加快生產MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.68,0:05:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅姆斐拉裡看來有不穩的動靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.15,0:05:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不能信任人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.52,0:05:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MD成為\N新戰士的時代來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.89,0:06:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老人家果然鎮定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.06,0:06:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空氣即將用完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.86,0:06:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意識快要失去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.53,0:06:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還末消滅OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到就這樣子死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.03,0:06:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看一眼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.10,0:06:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新出現的鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.87,0:06:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神和神龍的改良還未完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.31,0:06:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.45,0:06:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.99,0:06:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到…真的就此死去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.47,0:06:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五飛…好威風啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.90,0:06:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的[地獄死神]…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.34,0:06:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了它…OZ根本不堪一擊啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.74,0:06:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做甚麼…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.51,0:07:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死了嗎…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.71,0:07:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五飛…我好寂寞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.35,0:07:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪我直到最後啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.19,0:07:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…在停止呼吸嗎…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.03,0:07:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說這叫龜息…嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.10,0:07:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙真厲害…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.23,0:07:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未到最後不放棄希望…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.17,0:07:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊…我不能就此死去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以輸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.99,0:07:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對你那樣說也沒用呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.23,0:07:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我要打倒你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.96,0:07:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要動手的就快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.00,0:07:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒打算和敵人囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.92,0:08:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為你錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.49,0:08:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.36,0:08:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰鬥是沒必要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.47,0:08:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦!快離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜葉特要爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.67,0:08:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.44,0:08:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.31,0:08:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.48,0:08:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛!停手!特洛瓦他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.47,0:09:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以甚麼形式也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.94,0:09:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衛星和OZ聯手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.31,0:09:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣表示一場戰爭已經完結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.01,0:09:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時，我們的任務也完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.98,0:09:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對為了衛星而戰的我們來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.89,0:09:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衛星改變了主意是遺憾的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.36,0:09:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這是戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.52,0:09:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只有接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.96,0:09:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後是被遺棄的士兵的問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.23,0:09:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是我們心裡的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未成熟的我們身為士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.74,0:09:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直過於倚靠完美的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.94,0:09:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於一直認真戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以即使只有自己一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.98,0:09:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也認為能改變這時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.01,0:09:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特爾，那不只你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.98,0:09:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.08,0:09:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那種心把仁慈的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.92,0:09:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,推進痛苦的死胡同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們心裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們自己要戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.56,0:10:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且一定要殘酷地找出結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.60,0:10:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使一直以來的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.63,0:10:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成無意義也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.47,0:10:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來不得不承認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.90,0:10:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是…這時代\N不再需要的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.71,0:10:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受時代吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.88,0:10:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後，變回仁慈的卡特爾好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.95,0:10:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉這機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.12,0:10:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能令卡特爾你冷靜下來就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.59,0:10:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉這機會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.56,0:10:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.40,0:10:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛!放開我!特洛瓦會死!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.44,0:10:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，是你殺死他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.01,0:10:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.75,0:10:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瘋狂的傢伙…我要把他殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.19,0:11:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你就打倒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後去救特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.32,0:11:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你以那麼\N天真的想法在戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.46,0:11:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白費了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.26,0:11:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦的死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.47,0:11:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特爾…我要…殺死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.65,0:11:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.72,0:11:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要太過為難卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.19,0:11:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.47,0:11:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的科技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.27,0:11:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉著我們羅姆斐拉財團的財力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.24,0:11:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開花結果的時候來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.21,0:11:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OZ終於完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.75,0:12:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MD的量產準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.62,0:12:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為支配階級的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把MD佈署在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.02,0:12:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各國的紛爭地域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.89,0:12:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉著告訴全世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.06,0:12:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們擁有多強大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.89,0:12:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賜予全世界秩序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.90,0:12:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後再次迎接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.73,0:12:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古老良好傳統和禮法的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.77,0:12:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,統一全世界吧!各位!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.08,0:12:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯，今後OZ也拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.78,0:12:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾麥優侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對羅姆斐拉財團要走的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.12,0:12:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不敢茍同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.42,0:12:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古老良好傳統是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.43,0:12:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類的深奧感情構成的歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.00,0:12:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我覺得戰鬥是美麗的同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.80,0:12:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會申訴生命是平等的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.14,0:13:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會向逝去的靈魂表示哀悼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.91,0:13:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為人類須要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.54,0:13:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並非絕對的勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.51,0:13:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是戰鬥的姿態和理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，羅姆斐拉財團使用MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.89,0:13:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種無心的戰鬥兵器\N建立的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.46,0:13:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會成為被後世不恥的文化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.19,0:13:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.46,0:13:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讚揚不能不戰鬥的人性的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.00,0:13:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得宇宙衛星的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不知道那傳統的無知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.90,0:13:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所產生的可憐牢騷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.87,0:13:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!死神!不要輕易被毀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.41,0:13:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.18,0:13:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二次演習開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.13,0:13:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.00,0:14:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.44,0:14:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的…眼淚嗎…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.17,0:14:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，從那種恐懼中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.44,0:14:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超越我的理想的新戰士誕生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.21,0:14:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是鋼彈的駕駛員們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.22,0:14:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.56,0:14:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們怕死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.79,0:14:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，不要戰鬥就行了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.13,0:14:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在他們充滿純真的感情前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.40,0:14:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳統會看不清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.41,0:14:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去要保護的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.41,0:14:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兼且被保護的人出賣的戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.98,0:14:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在歷史上是敗者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.41,0:14:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，他們沒有那種認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.85,0:14:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們自己反而還充滿戰意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是為了有奇蹟發生的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.42,0:15:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在做現在能做的最佳事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果一切瘋狂的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.57,0:15:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就會相信自己而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.57,0:15:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人被認為美麗的\N感情總是悲哀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重視的傳統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.65,0:15:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會在弱者們的叫喊中消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥裡的勝者在歷史中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.98,0:15:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要畫上稱為衰退的休止符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.05,0:15:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有朝氣的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會從敗者之中培養出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.46,0:15:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯，你想說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.19,0:15:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想成為敗者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.66,0:15:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，你是說羅姆斐拉財團總部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.47,0:15:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從你手上沒收OZ比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.74,0:15:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們做不出血腥的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.95,0:15:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也因為你一直以來有功績
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.42,0:15:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你軟禁\N在羅姆斐拉財團總部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.59,0:16:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使用扮成忘記戰鬥的槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.46,0:16:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射穿敵人的胸膛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.80,0:16:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也不會令我感動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋並非不正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.50,0:16:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們的心是自由的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.24,0:16:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月面基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進入巴爾吉雷射砲\N的直接射程內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.78,0:16:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進攻方向發現月面基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.91,0:16:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佈署的MD陶拉斯部隊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.08,0:16:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它們已經準備攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.79,0:16:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡到月面基地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.15,0:16:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾蒂‧安小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.82,0:16:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴爾吉的移動\N不在今日的程序裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.73,0:16:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MD差一點就會開始攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫不留情的兵器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.93,0:16:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是MD嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.67,0:16:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.47,0:16:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的量產系統也完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.91,0:16:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.54,0:16:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為地球帶來秩序的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.94,0:16:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最強士兵的完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.31,0:17:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看來明白特列斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.78,0:17:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭MD的心情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.92,0:17:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.15,0:17:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯大人愛別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.49,0:17:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也愛人的死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.79,0:17:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡有強烈打動\N人類感情的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.29,0:17:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡給予的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.30,0:17:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對戰鬥的肯定和否定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.10,0:17:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,興奮的感情會引致極端的選擇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.77,0:17:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受死亡才是戰士正確的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.08,0:17:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是弱者的想法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.55,0:17:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在誕生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.25,0:17:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名為MD的不死戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.02,0:17:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在建立\N超越死亡的戰鬥歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.76,0:17:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茲巴洛夫，你沒發覺嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.46,0:17:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MD並非超越死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它們是你們害怕死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擔任替身的人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.97,0:17:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不可能參加\N預料會輸的戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.01,0:18:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勝敗沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.57,0:18:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷戰鬥會令感情經歷鍛煉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.78,0:18:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逝去的靈魂得到回報的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.28,0:18:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終有一日也會來臨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.18,0:18:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我不能理解的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.12,0:18:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你和我才成為敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.56,0:18:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指示MD進行對要塞戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.27,0:18:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們會用巴爾吉雷射砲攻擊基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.74,0:18:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想不到巴爾吉是餌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.21,0:18:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果用巴爾吉雷射砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.44,0:18:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能預測月面基地的損毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.45,0:18:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別被攻陷啊，巴爾吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會須要太久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十部里歐突破防衛線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.79,0:18:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻止巴爾吉而疏於防守的閘口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.83,0:18:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被集中攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.53,0:18:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MD在這裡的佈署
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.46,0:18:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全被知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.83,0:19:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會有趣起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.74,0:19:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佔據MD\N生產工場，拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.17,0:19:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特校妳去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去釋放鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.48,0:19:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯大人也希望那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.32,0:19:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人沒有追擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.73,0:19:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，死守這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.49,0:19:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊…隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.86,0:19:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.90,0:19:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新型機已經能動了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.61,0:19:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能趕得上就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.85,0:19:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕得及也好，我只須再處死他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.85,0:19:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，到時我也勞煩你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.65,0:19:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在OZ的錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.12,0:20:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是染血的過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.63,0:20:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，開槍!茲巴洛夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了肯定你自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.74,0:20:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾蒂‧安小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.47,0:20:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.47,0:20:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為士兵，我太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但身為人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.71,0:20:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打算堅強地活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.97,0:20:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成度70%，還不能盡情戰鬥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.74,0:20:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能活下去已經是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會奢求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.75,0:20:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要逃嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.01,0:20:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先要報仇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.23,0:21:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令一切瘋狂的愛是痛苦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.30,0:21:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,純真的心在找不到\N答案的世界裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.44,0:21:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在痛苦嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.64,0:21:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得那模樣可愛的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.78,0:21:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會因為自己的無能而焦急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.51,0:22:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,及被消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.45,0:22:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，勇敢的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.88,0:22:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你們繼續發放光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.52,0:22:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而今後也請讓我愛你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.33,0:22:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.04,0:22:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.04,0:22:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.04,0:22:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.04,0:22:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.54,0:22:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.04,0:23:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.54,0:23:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.04,0:23:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.04,0:23:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.83,0:23:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回予告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.64,0:23:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨著特列斯被軟禁
